Sazka’s Largest Shareholder Plans to Dismiss Husak, CTK Reports

-- B y   L e n k a   P o n i k e l s k a
-- 
2011-07-14T13:50:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-14/sazka-s-largest-shareholder-plans-to-dismiss-husak-ctk-reports.html
Czech Sports Association, the
largest shareholder of Sazka AS, plans to dismiss the company’s
former Chief Executive Officer Ales Husak from the board of
directors at a shareholders meeting,  CTK  reported, citing Pavel Koran, the association’s chief.  Sazka plans to hold the shareholders’ meeting on July 19,
the newswire said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lenka Ponikelska in Prague 
 lponikelska1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at   jagomez@bloomberg.net  